               7) Dungeon - CLANGERS
@endnode               
@node "MONTY PYTHON'S FLYING CIRCUS"
MONTY PYTHON'S FLYING CIRCUS

When you get onto the high score table, enter your name as 'SEMPRINI'.  When
you start the game, the options menu will now have the option of making the
hidden bonuses invisible or visible.  When you die, you will start the game
on the last level you were on.
@endnode
@node "MOONSHINE RACERS"
MOONSHINE RACERS

During play, type "CHICKEN MASALA" and use the 'F10' key to advance to the
next level.
@endnode
@node "MOONSTONE"
MOONSTONE

Take a trip to Stonehenge, keep hold of any valuable items and position the
pointer at either the word "GOLD", "STRENGTH", "CONSTITUTION" or "ENDURANCE"
and tap the fire button.  The druids should continue the ceremony and you
will get an extra life without losing any items whatsoever.

Amiga Power magazine says that when you enter Stonehenge and you have to
offer a magical item to Danu, click on the Strength (STR) for an extra life.
Do this as often as you like.
@endnode
@node "MORTAL KOMBAT"
MORTAL KOMBAT

On the screen where you select to start the game or options, type:"CATHULU"
and the new selection "CHEATMODE" will appear.  Enter the cheat menu and
type: "RJC" and a statistics screen will appear, press 'Space' to return to
the selection menu.  On the screen that tells you about codes, type:
"VAMPIRE" and the words will turn white and you should hear a sound.  This
will turn off the blood.
@endnode
@node "MOUTHMAN"
MOUTHMAN

On the title screen, hold down the Right Mouse Button, the Left Mouse Button,
the Fire Button and push the Joystick Left for 5 seconds or until the title
screen comes back.  Select the empty space from the menu to enter the level
editor.
@endnode
